name: Liquid Highlighter - Gold
description:
This is the most natural looking highlighting product you will ever own. Available in a rose and gold tone these two shades will work for everyone. With our easy to use tapered applicator, just dab onto your cupid's bow to bring out the fullness of your lips. Use on your cheek bone, forehead and chin to enhance the natural beauty of your face.

Comes with tapered applicator for precision touchup
Paraben, talc, and gluten-free
Vegan and cruelty-free
5 mL / 0.17 fl oz
Made in Canada

Ingredients: Aqua, cyclomethicone, cyclohexasiloxane, mica, ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate, panax ginseng root extract, butylene glycol, cyclopentasiloxane, peg-10 dimethicone, disteardimonium hectorite, cetyl ethylhexanoate, dimethicone/vinyl dimethicone crosspolymer, dicaprylyl carbonate, phenyl trimethicone, glycerin, methyl methacrylate crosspolymer, lauryl peg-9 polydimethylsiloxyethyl dimethicone, tribehenin, sodium chloride, urea, sodium pca, trehalose, polyquaternium-51, sodium hyaluronate, aloe barbadensis leaf extract, hydrolyzed conchiolin protein, magnesium stearate, phenoxyethanol, 1,2-hexanediol, fragrance, camellia sinensis leaf extract, glycyrrhiza uralensis (licorice) root extract, disodium edta, may contain: titanium dioxide, ci77491, ci77492, ci77499, yellow 6 lake, red 40 lake, red 6 lake, red 7 lake, red 28 lake
